---
title: Swedish-Inspired Beyond Meat® Burgers with Potato Coins and Dilly Mayo
description: You don't need to buy build-it-yourself furniture to get a taste of Swedish meatballs for dinner! This cheeky Beyond Meat® burger is cloaked in a creamy mushroom sauce with some potato coins and dilly dip on the side.
